OL,6,FThe owner of first Afro-Caribbean
OL,7,Frestaurant says she has been the
OL,8,Fvictim of racial abuse, vandalism and
OL,9,Fphysical attacks.
OL,11,FMaya Mihoc opened Big Maya's Jerk on
OL,12,FHoxton Road in August last year.
OL,14,FShe said while diners were impressed,
OL,15,Fonline abuse soon followed.
OL,17,FMaya told ITV News she has received
OL,18,Fabusive messages, including monkey and
OL,19,Fbanana emojis, and reviews about her
OL,20,Ffood on social media from people who
OL,21,Fhad never been to her restaurant.
