OL,6,FIn January a window was smashed. In
OL,7,Fanother incident a man ran into the
OL,8,Fpremises and threw a drink in her face
OL,9,Fbefore running away.
OL,11,F"Someone ran in the door and threw a
OL,12,Fdrink on me and I initially thought it
OL,13,Fwas acid," Maya said.
OL,15,F"Just when I thought it couldn't get
OL,16,Fworse, someone threw a bottle through
OL,17,Fmy open window at home. It happened in
OL,18,Fdaylight, at 1.30 in the afternoon.
