OL,3,COwner of town's first Caribbean
OL,4,Crestaurant racially abused
OL,6,F"I know I present strong most of the
OL,7,Ftime, but ultimately I'm just a human.
OL,8,FContinuously being harassed really
OL,9,Fimpacts me."
OL,11,FMaya has vowed to beat the racist
OL,12,Fbullies she faces in person and online
OL,13,Fand has launched a crowdfunding
OL,14,Fcampaign to increase security at the
OL,15,Frestaurant.
OL,17,FShe hopes to install CCTV and shutters
OL,18,Ffor the front windows to prevent any
OL,19,Fmore criminal damage.
