OL,3,COwner of town's first Caribbean
OL,4,Crestaurant racially abused
OL,6,F"It's the community that supports me
OL,7,Fand that tells me that they want me to
OL,8,Fstay which give me the power to want
OL,9,Fto fight and stay here."
OL,11,FNorth Yorkshire Police said it had
OL,12,Freceived a report from Maya after her
OL,13,Fwindows were smashed and has urged
OL,14,Fanyone else who believes they may be
OL,15,Fthe victim of a hate crime to come
OL,16,Fforward.
OL,18,FIt said in a statement: "We sent
OL,19,Fofficers to speak with the business
OL,20,Fowner who believes that they were
OL,21,Ftargeted due to their race.
