OL,6,F"As part of the investigation into the
OL,7,Fincident we carried out an extensive
OL,8,FCCTV trawl in the area and issued a
OL,9,Fmedia appeal to ask the public to come
OL,10,Fforward with information.
OL,12,F"North Yorkshire Police believes that
OL,13,Ftargeting people because of who they
OL,14,Fare is completely unacceptable."
